nate on "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-08-07"},"text":"Aug. 7, 1992","children":[],"tail":", to reflect the probable intent of Congress."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was formerly classified to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s11710"},"text":"section 11710 of this title","children":[],"tail":" prior to the general amendment of this chapter by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/396"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–396","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/579"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–579","children":[],"tail":" and "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/690"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–690","children":[],"tail":" enacted substantially identical sections. The text of this section is based on "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/579/s12"},"text":"section 12 of Pub. L. 100–579","children":[],"tail":", as subsequently amended."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idbf57db17-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2010—Par. (2)(H). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/148"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–148","children":[],"tail":", which directed the amendment of section 12(2) of the Native Hawaiian Health Care Act of 1988 by adding subpar. (H), was executed by making the amendment to this section, which is section 12 of the Native Hawaiian Health Care Improvement Act, to reflect the probable intent of Congress."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1992—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/396"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–396","children":[],"tail":" amended section generally. Prior to amendment, section related to severability."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
